    76	  LLM distillation → index distilled units → re-measure); PRF/D2 deprioritized. HITL scope decision (fork b).
    77	- **form_lift_material** ⇒ strong corroboration for the memory-formation lever.
    78	This is the input to the Slice-30 resolution + the 0.8.4 (GraphRAG) / HippoRAG sequencing.

