   114	
   115	    ``point`` = mean; ``ci_lo/ci_hi`` = percentile paired bootstrap (reuses the m1
   116	    helpers, seed-deterministic); ``mde`` = normal-approx paired minimum detectable
   117	    effect ``(z.975+z.80)·sd/√n`` (the §5 power quantity the rule gates on). ``n`` =
   118	    sample size. n==0 → all-``None``; n==1 → degenerate point CI, mde ``None``."""
   119	    import numpy as np
